{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "让我们看看如何构建和使用组件级评估",
      "from": 0.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 3.98
    },
    {
      "content": "在我们的研究代理示例中",
      "from": 3.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 6.74
    },
    {
      "content": "我们提到研究代理有时会遗漏关键点",
      "from": 6.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 10.64
    },
    {
      "content": "但如果问题是网络搜索",
      "from": 10.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 13.26
    },
    {
      "content": "每次我们更换网络搜索引擎时",
      "from": 13.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 15.78
    },
    {
      "content": "需要重新运行整个工作流程以获得性能指标",
      "from": 15.78,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 20.6
    },
    {
      "content": "但这种评估成本很高",
      "from": 20.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 23.42
    },
    {
      "content": "此外这是一个相当复杂的流程",
      "from": 23.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 26.9
    },
    {
      "content": "即使网络搜索有所改善",
      "from": 26.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 29.48
    },
    {
      "content": "其他组件的随机性引入的噪声",
      "from": 29.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 32.92
    },
    {
      "content": "会让观察网络搜索质量的小改进变得更困难",
      "from": 32.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 37.91
    },
    {
      "content": "作为仅使用端到端评估的替代方案",
      "from": 37.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 41.37
    },
    {
      "content": "我会考虑构建专门评估网络搜索组件质量的评估",
      "from": 41.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 47.74
    },
    {
      "content": "例如",
      "from": 47.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 48.46
    },
    {
      "content": "衡量网络搜索结果的质量",
      "from": 48.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 50.44
    },
    {
      "content": "可以创建一组黄金标准网络资源",
      "from": 50.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 53.22
    },
    {
      "content": "对于少数查询",
      "from": 53.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 55.6
    },
    {
      "content": "让专家指出这些是最权威的资源",
      "from": 55.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 58.74
    },
    {
      "content": "如果有人在搜索互联网时",
      "from": 58.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 60.58
    },
    {
      "content": "应该找到这些网页",
      "from": 60.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 62.32
    },
    {
      "content": "或者这些网页中的任何一个都很好",
      "from": 62.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 64.64
    },
    {
      "content": "然后可以编写代码捕获",
      "from": 64.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 66.919
    },
    {
      "content": "网络搜索输出与黄金标准资源的匹配程度",
      "from": 66.919,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 72.89
    },
    {
      "content": "信息检索的标准指标",
      "from": 72.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 75.31
    },
    {
      "content": "F1分数",
      "from": 75.31,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 76.4
    },
    {
      "content": "无需在意细节",
      "from": 76.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 77.56
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你不了解这些术语",
      "from": 77.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 78.52
    },
    {
      "content": "但存在标准指标可衡量网页列表",
      "from": 78.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 82.7
    },
    {
      "content": "由网络搜索返回",
      "from": 82.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 83.82
    },
    {
      "content": "与专家确定内容的重叠程度",
      "from": 83.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 87.28
    },
    {
      "content": "是否与这些黄金标准资源匹配",
      "from": 87.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 90.02
    },
    {
      "content": "现在你已掌握评估网络搜索组件质量的方法",
      "from": 90.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 94.9
    },
    {
      "content": "当你调整网络搜索的相关参数或超参数时",
      "from": 94.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 100.35
    },
    {
      "content": "例如切换不同的网络搜索引擎",
      "from": 100.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 103.23
    },
    {
      "content": "比如尝试谷歌、必应和Dr",
      "from": 103.23,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 105.63
    },
    {
      "content": "Go和Tville",
      "from": 105.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 106.81
    },
    {
      "content": "以及Com和其他引擎",
      "from": 106.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 107.99
    },
    {
      "content": "或者调整结果数量",
      "from": 107.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 110.11
    },
    {
      "content": "或日期范围",
      "from": 110.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 111.76
    },
    {
      "content": "这些变化能让YaSa网络搜索引擎快速判断",
      "from": 111.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 115.38
    },
    {
      "content": "网络搜索组件质量是否提升并实现渐进改进",
      "from": 115.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 122.07
    },
    {
      "content": "然后",
      "from": 122.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 122.41
    },
    {
      "content": "当然",
      "from": 122.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 122.91
    },
    {
      "content": "在宣布完成之前",
      "from": 122.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 124.51
    },
    {
      "content": "最好运行端到端评估",
      "from": 124.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 126.89
    },
    {
      "content": "确保经过长时间调优网络搜索系统后",
      "from": 126.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 129.94
    },
    {
      "content": "整体系统性能确实提升",
      "from": 129.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 133.12
    },
    {
      "content": "但在调整这些超参数过程中",
      "from": 133.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 136.58
    },
    {
      "content": "可以逐个进行",
      "from": 136.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 137.12
    },
    {
      "content": "只需专注于单个组件即可大幅提升效率",
      "from": 137.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 140.62
    },
    {
      "content": "与其每次都需要重新运行端到端测试",
      "from": 140.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 144.69
    },
    {
      "content": "因此组件级测试可以更清晰地定位特定错误",
      "from": 144.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 150.57
    },
    {
      "content": "它能明确告诉你是否在提升网页搜索组件性能",
      "from": 150.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 153.96
    },
    {
      "content": "或者你正在开发的任何组件",
      "from": 153.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 155.62
    },
    {
      "content": "并避免整体系统复杂性中的干扰噪声",
      "from": 155.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 160.82
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你在涉及不同团队的项目中工作",
      "from": 160.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 164.15
    },
    {
      "content": "专注于不同组件",
      "from": 164.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 165.79
    },
    {
      "content": "单个团队也可以拥有自己",
      "from": 165.79,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 168.83
    },
    {
      "content": "非常明确的优化指标无需考虑其他组件",
      "from": 168.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 173.18
    },
    {
      "content": "这能让团队专注于更小的",
      "from": 173.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 175.42
    },
    {
      "content": "更具针对性的问题",
      "from": 175.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 177.23
    },
    {
      "content": "从而加快进度，当你决定改进某个组件时",
      "from": 177.23,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 182.269
    },
    {
      "content": "考虑是否值得建立组件",
      "from": 182.269,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 185.029
    },
    {
      "content": "智能评估",
      "from": 185.029,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 185.869
    },
    {
      "content": "以及这是否能更快提升该组件性能",
      "from": 185.869,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 190.75
    },
    {
      "content": "现在",
      "from": 190.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 191.43
    },
    {
      "content": "你可能想知道如果决定改进某个组件",
      "from": 191.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 195.33
    },
    {
      "content": "如何实际让该组件表现更好",
      "from": 195.33,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 199.51
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们在下一视频中看一些实例",
      "from": 199.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 202.75
    }
  ]
}